## 4. Architecture Overview

```
Input (at inference):
  Pocket point cloud — atoms within 10Å of ligand centroid
  Ligand graph — topology only (atom types, bonds), NO coordinates

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Stage 1: Featurization  (precomputed, saved to disk)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Ligand nodes:   [atom_type_onehot(10), charge(1), hybridization(3),
                 aromaticity(1), degree(1), in_ring(1)]  → 17-dim
Ligand edges:   [bond_type(4), conjugated(1), in_ring(1)]  → 6-dim
Pocket nodes:   [element_onehot(8), is_backbone(1), residue_onehot(20)] → 29-dim
Pocket edges:   RBF(||xi - xj||, 16 basis functions) → 16-dim (dist < 6Å)
Cross edges:    ligand atom ↔ pocket atom, k=4 nearest, RBF dist features

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Stage 2: EGNN  (4 layers, hidden_dim=64)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Each EGNN layer:
  m_ij = MLP([h_i, h_j, ||x_i-x_j||², edge_attr])   # message
  x_i' = x_i + Σ_j (x_i - x_j) · MLP(m_ij)          # coord update
  h_i' = MLP([h_i, Σ_j m_ij])                         # node update

Pocket coords are fixed (not updated by coord update).
Cross-graph messages flow pocket→ligand only.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Stage 3: Flow Matching
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Training:
  x_0 ~ N(0, I)                        # Gaussian noise
  x_1 = crystal coords                 # ground truth
  t ~ Uniform(0, 1)
  x_t = (1-t)·x_0 + t·x_1             # linear interpolant
  target = x_1 - x_0                   # constant velocity field
  loss = ||EGNN(x_t, pocket, t) - target||²

Inference (20-step Euler):
  x_0 ~ N(0, I)
  for t in linspace(0, 1, 20):
      x = x + (1/20) · EGNN(x, pocket, t)

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Stage 4: Post-processing
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Assign generated coords to RDKit mol
  Chirality correction via AssignStereochemistryFromCoords
  MMFF94 energy calculation (score only, no minimization)
  Bond length sanity check (flag outliers)
```

