## 9. Evaluation Suite

### 9.1 RMSD (geometric fidelity)
```python
def kabsch_rmsd(P, Q):
    Pc, Qc = P - P.mean(0), Q - Q.mean(0)
    U, _, Vt = torch.linalg.svd(Pc.T @ Qc)
    d = torch.linalg.det(Vt.T @ U.T)
    R = Vt.T @ torch.diag(torch.tensor([1., 1., d])) @ U.T
    return ((Pc @ R.T - Qc)**2).sum(-1).mean().sqrt().item()
# Report: median, mean, % < 1/2/5Å over 50 test complexes
```

### 9.2 MMFF94 Strain Energy (physical validity — the key metric)
```python
def mmff94_energy(mol, coords):
    conf = mol.GetConformer()
    for i, (x,y,z) in enumerate(coords): conf.SetAtomPosition(i, (x,y,z))
    ff = AllChem.MMFFGetMoleculeForceField(mol, AllChem.MMFFGetMoleculeProperties(mol))
    return ff.CalcEnergy() if ff else None
# Report: E_generated / E_ETKDG ratio (target ≤ 1.3)
```

